msgid "Graphic Tablets"
msgstr "绘图板"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing_blender/hardware.rst:13
msgid ""
"Graphics tablets can be used to provide a more traditional method of "
"controlling the mouse cursor using a pen. This can help to provide a "
"more familiar experience for artists who are used to painting and "
"drawing with similar tools, as well as provide additional controls such "
"as pressure sensitivity."
msgstr ""
"因为数位板有笔这个元素，所以使用它可以用更为传统的方式控制鼠标指针，这对"
"习惯用笔工作的艺术工作者来说是个例好消息，而且数位板还能提供压感等参数。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing_blender/hardware.rst:20
msgid ""
"If you are using a graphic tablet instead of a mouse and pressure "
"sensitivity doesn't work properly, try to place the mouse pointer in the "
"Blender window and then unplug/replug your graphic tablet. This might "
"help."
msgstr ""
"如果你用数位板代替鼠标工作的时候，发现数位板的压感不正常，你可以试着先把"
"指针放置在Blender界面中，再把数位板的线头拔出来吹吹灰插回去，这也许能管"
"用。"

